      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Get ready to drive away in a true masterpiece! This car is in absolute mint condition, looking and feeling just as spectacular as the day it left the showroom. From its flawless paint to its pristine interior and top-tier performance, this vehicle has been meticulously cared for and is ready for its next proud owner!",
